OL,3,CKen Skates confirmed as Welsh Labour
OL,4,Cleader
OL,6,FKen Skates has been confirmed as
OL,7,Fleader of Welsh Labour.
OL,9,FHe became interim leader in May,
OL,10,Ffollowing Eluned Morgan's resignation.
OL,12,FWelsh Labour had led Wales since the
OL,13,FSenedd was established as the National
OL,14,FAssembly for Wales in 1999, and was
OL,15,Fthe largest party in the country for
OL,16,Fmore than a century.
OL,18,FMs Morgan quit as Welsh Labour leader
OL,19,Fafter losing her seat in the election.
