OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1784229523
OL,3,CKen Skates confirmed as Welsh Labour
OL,4,Cleader
OL,6,FWelsh Labour opened nominations for a
OL,7,Fpermanent replacement last Thursday,
OL,8,Fstarting with nominations from the
OL,9,FSenedd Labour Group.
OL,11,FAll nine members of the group
OL,12,Fnominated Mr Skates, confirming his
OL,13,Fappointment as leader.
OL,15,F"I am deeply honoured to have the
OL,16,Funanimous backing of my colleagues in
OL,17,Fthe Senedd in seeking the leadership
OL,18,Fof Welsh Labour," he said.
OL,26,@wD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/5
