CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1784229523
OL,3,CKen Skates confirmed as Welsh Labour
OL,4,Cleader
OL,6,F"I joined the party as a 14-year-old,
OL,7,Fand my belief still stands that no
OL,8,Fchild's future should be determined by
OL,9,Ftheir background. That no young person
OL,10,Fshould be judged on anything other
OL,11,Fthan the efforts they make and the
OL,12,Fdecency they show to others.
OL,14,F"The Labour movement for me is a
OL,15,Fmovement for fairness, justice,
OL,16,Fsecurity and liberty. It is a movement
OL,17,Fthat seeks to empower people and
OL,18,Fcommunities, to fight against
OL,19,Finjustice, intolerance, nepotism and
OL,20,Fcruelty."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU|D@IO]
