OL,3,CKen Skates confirmed as Welsh Labour
OL,4,Cleader
OL,6,FMr Skates, 50, was first elected in
OL,7,F2011 and held roles including
OL,8,FTransport Secretary and Economy and
OL,9,FInfrastructure Secretary in the former
OL,10,FWelsh Labour government.
OL,12,FHe was re-elected to the Senedd for
OL,13,Fthe new constituency of Fflint Wrecsam
OL,14,Fin May.
OL,16,FDeputy leader of Welsh Labour, Carolyn
OL,17,FHarris MP, said: "I offer my warm
OL,18,Fcongratulations to Ken.
OL,26,@yD@ROU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/5
