OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,437,430,260,120,000,100
PN,43605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F436A1784229523
OL,3,CKen Skates confirmed as Welsh Labour
OL,4,Cleader
OL,6,F"He has my full backing as he
OL,7,Fundertakes the big task ahead of him -
OL,8,Flistening, learning, rebuilding and
OL,9,Fdoing that crucial job of holding
OL,10,FPlaid Cymru, and Reform UK, to account
OL,11,Fin the Senedd.
OL,13,F"I have no doubt he has the energy,
OL,14,Fthoughtfulness and optimism to take us
OL,15,Fforward and I look forward to working
OL,16,Falongside him."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/5
